    "Timeliness.",
    "Currently, the coverage time of most pre-training corpora is relatively outdated, lacking recent knowledge and making it challenging to achieve periodic updates.",
    "This results in inaccurate generation or outdated information and being unable to respond to recent content.",
    "Common Crawl, for instance, continually crawls the latest webpage data, but the majority is in English.",
    "Other types of data require reacquisition and preprocessing when updates are needed."
